ISLAMABAD, Oct 28 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Thursday that in view of the situation arising out of the illegal activities of a banned party, Prime Minister Imran Khan has convened a meeting of the National Security Committee tomorrow(Friday).
In a tweet, he said that other issues related to national security would also be considered in the meeting.
